        <question id="q1">
            <body><p>Which values of X would be included if we
                    want<?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101121T110133-0500" content=":"?>
                    at most 4? Choose <em>yes</em> if the value is included. Choose <em>no</em> if
